\usepackage{mathrsfs}
\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
\begin{document}
}{}$$\begin{equation*}\begin{array}{*{20}{c}} {\forall g\ {\rm and}\ c,}&{\ {n_{g,c}} = \mathop \sum \nolimits_{i\ } g \in c;\ \ }&{\ {r_{g,c}} = \mathop \sum \nolimits_{i\ } g \notin c;\ } \end{array}\end{equation*}$$\end{document}where i are the samples in cohorts A and B (Figure 1).

